      "sector": "public_sector",
      "title": "Municipal login with attribute-based credentials",
      "summary": "Citizens log in to their municipal account and securely share only the personal attributes a service actually needs, using an attribute-based wallet. The municipality acts as the relying party and verifies the presented attributes over the IRMA protocol. This is one of the first production implementations of attribute-based authentication in Dutch municipal services, showing that privacy-friendly login at scale is possible today.",
